title: Bug 7945: Search results not being selected in external jar
description: Bug 7945: Search results are not being selected in external jar Build 200201151. When searching for references to this field, the search should return 3 matches in the method getTempDir().
OB: When searching for references to the field in the external jar, the search results should be selected and displayed correctly.
EB: You should get 3 matches in the method getTempDir() when searching for references to this field in the external jar.
SR: Ensure that the search functionality is working correctly in the external jar, and that the search results are selected and displayed accurately.
